high_descs: Walk over to the counter.
Pick up the butter knife off of the counter.
Turn right and walk forward, then turn left to face the counter.
Put the butter knife in the white mug on the counter.
Pick up the mug with the butter knife in it off of the counter.
Turn around and take a step forward, then turn right and walk towards the wall, then turn right to face the sink.
Put the mug with the butter knife in it into the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a mug with a butter knife in it into the sink.

high_descs: Walk forward to the kitchen counter
Pick up the butter knife from the counter
Walk a couple feet right then turn back left to face the counter
Put the knife in the white mug on the counter
Pick up the white mug from the counter
Turn left and walk over to the kitchen sink
Put the mug down in the sink
anns.task_desc: Put the mug with knife in the kitchen sink

high_descs: Walk ahead to the counter.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Take a step right.
Place the knife in the white mug.
Pick up the white mug.
Take a couple steps left.
Place the mug in the front left corner of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a mug with a knife in it in a sink.
